                            <li>The date and time of your visit to the sites.</li>
                            <li>The amount of time you spend using the sites.</li>
                            <li>The Internet Protocol (IP) address used to connect your computer to the internet.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>Your computer and connection information such as your browser type and version, operating system and platform
                            This information is collected to enhance the site performance and end user experience. You can set your browser to reject cookies or to notify you when you are sent a cookie. To learn more about your ability to manage cookies and web beacons, please consult the privacy features in your browser.</p>
